libnotify: libnotify (Galago Desktop Notification Library)
libnotify:
libnotify: libnotify is a part of a desktop presence framework, designed to 
libnotify: transmit presence information between programs. To put it in simpler 
libnotify: terms, it takes information on who is online and their away/idle
libnotify: states from an instant messenger (such as gaim) or other similar
libnotify: programs and lets other programs (such as Ximian's Evolution) to
libnotify: make use of it. The advantage of such a framework is that it brings 
libnotify: your programs closer together.
